{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This session will help you take advantage of the Multi-Touch features available in iOS. You will learn practical information about Multi-Touch APIs, touch routing, gesture recognizers, as well as guidelines for interoperating with the system and other apps, and pointers for how to create complex real-world user interfaces which make great use of Multi-Touch."}],"kind":"article","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-118-making-the-most-of-multitouch-on-ios"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading":"WWDC11","role":"sampleCode","title":"Making the Most of Multi-Touch on iOS"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-118-Making-the-Most-of-MultiTouch-on-iOS","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"type":"reference","overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/118\/","isActive":true}},"references":{"WWDCNotes.png":{"type":"image","identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDCNotes.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/contrib